    ins_accountability: { text: "Intervened against State Farm in rate proceedings as a consumer advocate after the Palisades fire. Supports full payouts within 30 days of total loss — eliminating the 'delay and deny' culture. Would hold both the Department of Insurance and insurers accountable through structural reform, not just enforcement.", citations: ["ic14", "ic16"] },
