    ins_fair:           { text: "Would pursue tying homeowners insurance participation to broader market access: if an insurer operates in a region and sells other lines of insurance, it should be required to offer homeowners coverage there. Would support implementation of AB 226 (bonds to finance FAIR Plan claims) to strengthen its finances.", citations: ["ic3", "ic17"] },
